        <div class="footer">
            <h3>🛡️ Flex Gateway Policy Excellence</h3>
            <p>This comprehensive guide provides production-ready YAML configurations for all Flex Gateway policies. These configurations ensure enterprise-grade security, compliance, performance, and observability for your API infrastructure. All examples are tested and optimized for the Employee Onboarding Platform and can be adapted for various use cases.</p>
